  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jude, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- first I think there was the arm band, right, and then they changed it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know exactly when, but I think it came quickly after.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- and then also-- the Poles took advantage of it, too, because they could see-- many of them sided with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were-- as I said before, there was-- we knew that there was always some kind of anti-Semitism existing in Poland, but we-- but it was more in the open then, in the place where we lived.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so-- the Poles also-- there was a curfew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, of course, the Poles would turn Jews in [INAUDIBLE] run over to a city of [INAUDIBLE] or somebody, in the evening, at night time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we couldn't-- we were limited to-- not limited-- we were forbidden to be on the street or go any place beyond the curfew time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And it was really the turning point of the city of Oswiecim, when it became Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] The Polish army, I understand, had a big camp just outside of Oswiecim, which was part of-- must've been part of Auschwitz-- Oswiecim.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they-- so the Germans when they turned-- they had a-- they had all the buildings that he made to turn this place into a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know if it was a division or it was a like, here in our country, in the United States, they are like-- I was stationed in the Fourth Army, when I was in the Army during the Korean War.",
      "word_count": 41
    }
  ],
